messages.subject: My Son is a Star!
messages.msgSnippet: Julian is working on making a feature length movie with a bunch of other homeschooled teens. They started shooting last fall, and will continue this spring.
messages.messageBody:
Julian is working on making a feature length movie with a bunch of other
homeschooled teens. They started shooting last fall, and will continue this
spring. But one of the kids has put up this killer web site about the movie.

Julian's picture isn't up yet, because we are bad parents and haven't gotten
one yet, but the site is SO cool. Take a look. <A HREF="http://www.stirlingmovie.com/">http://www.stirlingmovie.com/</A>

Kathryn
